title: Micro USB Charging Cable 3M, USB A to Micro Android Charger Cable Braided Data Sync Cord for Samsung Galaxy J7,S7,S6…
html: Micro USB Charging Cable 3M, USB A to Micro Android Charger Cable Braided Data Sync Cord for Samsung Galaxy J7,S7,S6…
description: 【2.4A Faster Charging Speed & Data Sync】This Android 3 meters micro USB charging cable adopts 22 AWG tinned copper wire to support up to 2.4A high-speed charging and up to 480Mbps data transfer speed(support adapters of 12V/1.5A, 5V/2A, 5V2.4A, 5V/1A or 9V/2A). It will be your ideal charging cable no matter you are at home, office, car or during travel. 【Durable & Tangle-Free Design】With the protection of the durable nylon-braided jacket, our USB micro cables have 10000+ bend lifespan and are also free of tangle. The extended design of the cable end provides better protection against breakage over the years of use. Moreover, the premium aluminum-alloy housing not only offers better protection but also give it a fashionable look. 【Secure Connection】This 3meters micro charge cable features a stainless steel connector with phosphor bronze contacts to ensure a stable connection and a longer service life(can withstand 10000+ plug/unplug test). It will offer the perfect charge for your device and will not loose or fall off from the device like other those inferior micro cables do.
